name: Weather Station
body:
### Weather Station
This ASP.NET MVC application exports data from several XML files. The XML files contains data regarding weather conditions that has been collected all around Denmark. The application generetes different graphs and shows relevant statistics.

### Authors and Contributors
The following developers have been a part of this project: @backinblack10, @Elzamouri, @kagejohn and @danielwinther.
